flowchart TB
    A[Pipeline Start] --> B[Load Config + Preflight Validation]
    B --> C{Run Mode}

    C -->|Full mode| D[FASTQ Processing<br/>QC + Trim + Align + Variant Calling]
    C -->|Variant-only mode| E[External Variants Input<br/>VCF / VCF.GZ / CSV / TSV]

    E --> F[Normalize / Convert / Filter]
    D --> G[Final Filtered VCF]
    F --> G

    G --> H[Interpretation Layer<br/>Annotation + QC + Visuals + Enrichment]
    G --> I{PRS enabled?}
    I -->|Yes| J[PRS Scoring + QC + Distribution]
    I -->|No| K[Skip PRS]

    D --> L{RNA branch enabled?}
    L -->|Yes| M[RNA Quant + Differential Expression + Enrichment]
    L -->|No| N[Skip RNA branch]

    H --> O{AI enabled?}
    J --> O
    M --> O
    B --> O

    O -->|Yes| P[AI QC Anomaly + Variant Prioritization + Explainer]
    O -->|No| Q[Run Manifest + Final Outputs]
    P --> Q
    Q --> R[End]
